    if (BRAND_TO_MANUFACTURER_CODE[upperBrand]) {

    }

    // Then check manufacturer names
    for (const [name, code] of Object.entries(MANUFACTURER_NAMES_TO_CODES)) {
        if (name.includes(upperBrand) || upperBrand.includes(name)) {
            return code;
        }
    }

    return null;
}
